12
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:28,000
Turn it off.

13
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:40,759
This is my favorite sticker.

14
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,560
I'll stick it on your car.

15
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,360
