16
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:47,800
It's so ugly. Take it off.

17
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:49,318
Let me tell you.

18
00:02:49,319 --> 00:02:50,800
Only black is allowed in my car.

19
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:01,638
What are you doing?

20
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,879
Hurry up and take it off.

21
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:05,256
Can't you show some qualities of a good woman?

22
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,638
You can't wear this in my car.

23
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:08,199
Why do you have so many rules?

24
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,280
Do you think there are too many?

25
00:03:09,281 --> 00:03:10,401
If so, feel free to get out.

26
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,758
Miss.

27
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:22,599
Do you have rules in your car?

28
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,520
Yes.

29
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,758
Just one.

30
00:03:25,759 --> 00:03:26,840
Just be yourself.

31
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,879
Do you want some gum?

32
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,240
Miss.

33
00:03:37,639 --> 00:03:39,520
I think you're very happy.

34
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,360
Really?

35
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,520
The secret to a happy life...

36
00:03:46,039 --> 00:03:48,319
