37
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:52,599
Where do you want to go?

38
00:03:52,879 --> 00:03:53,960
The park.

39
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,319
The park?

40
00:03:55,919 --> 00:03:57,000
What do you want to do?

41
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:18,799
I was supposed to receive the documents five days ago,

42
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,336
but they have been delayed for no reason.

43
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,360
I just took a look.

44
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:23,776
The content we need to review is much more than we expected.

45
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,199
Isn't this a rip-off?

46
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:26,439
This is too much.

47
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,679
- Are they for real? - Are they for real?

48
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:31,050
Okay, I'll go to confront them in person.

49
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,120
Confront who?

50
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,800
Molina.

51
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,000
Come with me.

52
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:52,959
