81
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:09,039
Molina, you're mistaken.

82
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,120
He's just doing his job.

83
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:12,240
If he really pursues you,

84
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,480
