88
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,878
What did he ask about me?

89
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,560
He's concerned about you.

90
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:33,199
He even asked me if you're planning to study abroad.

91
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:37,199
