92
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,000
Bye, Sophie.

93
00:06:52,001 --> 00:06:53,360
- Okay, bye. - Bye.

94
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,438
(Let's have dinner together after you get off work.)

95
00:07:10,439 --> 00:07:12,239
(No rush. Just let me know when you're done.)

96
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:23,399
