109
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,439
Only a good chef can make it.

110
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:12,519
Timing is everything.

111
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,920
You've got a good understanding of food now.

112
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:18,120
