119
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,039
You eat so much.

120
00:08:47,450 --> 00:08:49,039
I'm so full.

121
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,799
Mr. Zhong.

122
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:57,519
Lately, someone has been pursuing me.

123
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,759
Really?

124
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:01,159
Is he handsome?

125
00:09:02,039 --> 00:09:04,090
Why don't you ask me if he's rich?

126
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:06,758
