127
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,798
He's super rich.

128
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:08,919
- Is that so? - It's true.

129
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,399
He's so rich...

130
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:14,239
