133
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:20,919
How about this?

134
00:09:21,039 --> 00:09:23,559
Give him more chances.

135
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,279
Who knows?

136
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,039
Maybe you'll like him.

137
00:09:29,450 --> 00:09:30,840
I don't like him.

138
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,240
However, in the past couple of days,

139
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,600
I've been giving it a lot of thought.

140
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,799
Perhaps finding...

141
00:09:44,279 --> 00:09:46,639
a well-off partner in the future...

142
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,759
would be a good choice.

143
00:09:49,210 --> 00:09:50,919
At least it wouldn't be so tiring, right?

144
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:53,209
I won't have to work overtime and stay up all night,

145
00:09:53,210 --> 00:09:54,919
juggling project after project.

146
00:09:55,090 --> 00:09:56,918
Do you know how tired I feel...

147
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:58,210
when I go home every day...

148
00:09:58,679 --> 00:10:01,210
and walk up those steps in high heels?

149
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,519
Why can't we...

150
00:10:04,210 --> 00:10:05,480
take a shortcut sometimes?

151
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:17,360
Actually, I worked really hard.

152
00:10:19,090 --> 00:10:21,519
I scrimped and saved to get to where I am today.

153
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,239
But sometimes,

154
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,399
when I look at the people around me,

155
00:10:30,450 --> 00:10:31,759
their background,

156
00:10:32,210 --> 00:10:33,360
education,

157
00:10:33,519 --> 00:10:34,879
qualifications, and connections...

158
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:37,360
