159
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:40,679
I don't even dare to consider...

160
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:42,399
studying abroad...

161
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,840
or getting more training.

162
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:50,159
I really envy them.

163
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,158
No matter what happens,

164
00:10:52,159 --> 00:10:54,519
they're always so carefree.

165
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,639
I can't do that.

166
00:10:58,919 --> 00:10:59,960
Actually,

167
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,919
I feel quite inferior.

168
00:11:05,759 --> 00:11:06,759
Han Su.

169
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,399
Think about it.

170
00:11:09,639 --> 00:11:13,159
They have a lot of external support,

171
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:17,440
but you're doing it all on your own.

172
00:11:18,559 --> 00:11:21,559
That proves that your abilities are stronger than theirs.

173
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:23,279
You have more potential.

174
00:11:23,919 --> 00:11:26,120
You're the best.

175
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:33,439
Really?

176
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,638
Yes.

177
00:11:34,639 --> 00:11:35,639
Here.

178
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,080
Here's a toast to you.

179
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:39,159
A toast to the best of you.

180
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,879
Mr. Zhong, let me ask you a question.

181
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:53,678
If your daughter meets a man with great qualities...

182
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:56,240
but she doesn't like him,

183
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:57,799
how would you advise her?

184
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:01,399
I've told them.

185
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,240
"As long as you like him,"

186
00:12:03,879 --> 00:12:05,879
"I'll like him too."

187
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:12,679
Being your daughter must be such a blessing.

188
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:14,919
Come on.

189
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,679
Don't drink too much.

190
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:33,399
It's not worth it for a love that's gone.

191
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,080
Who drinks for love?

192
00:12:39,159 --> 00:12:41,879
I drink for my own happiness.

193
00:12:45,879 --> 00:12:47,479
There are so many fun things to explore.

194
00:12:52,039 --> 00:12:53,518
Actually, I'm really curious.

195
00:12:53,519 --> 00:12:55,119
What do you ladies think...

196
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:57,599
