223
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,840
Sun Han Han, you can do it.

224
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,600
Okay.

225
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,879
Tomorrow, I'll start a new career.

226
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,840
Forget about multimedia and short videos.

227
00:14:36,039 --> 00:14:38,399
I'm going to cast a wide net on job sites.

228
00:14:38,639 --> 00:14:39,678
The world is huge.

229
00:14:39,679 --> 00:14:41,519
