Han Han.

562
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,159
You're not like that.

563
00:36:17,119 --> 00:36:18,239
You don't love him anymore.

564
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,480
Love him?

565
00:36:20,809 --> 00:36:21,960
I hate him.

566
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:26,769
I hate myself even more for loving him.

567
00:36:27,559 --> 00:36:28,840
The stupidest thing about me...

568
00:36:29,119 --> 00:36:30,440
is that I overestimated myself.

569
00:36:31,119 --> 00:36:32,599
That's why I fell into his trap...

570
00:36:32,679 --> 00:36:34,079
and have come this far.

571
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:37,000
I've driven myself into a corner.

572
00:36:37,599 --> 00:36:38,639
I'm a mess.

573
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:41,440
But how are you going to get rid of him?

574
00:36:43,039 --> 00:36:44,400
I've thought it through.

575
00:36:45,639 --> 00:36:48,119
If I want to get rid of Zhou Bin,

576
00:36:48,809 --> 00:36:50,880
I have to find someone more powerful than him.

577
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:52,880
Who?

578
00:36:53,599 --> 00:36:54,639
Zeng Cheng.

579
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:10,960
Han Han.

580
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:13,809
I really can't help you with this.

581
00:37:17,639 --> 00:37:19,199
It's okay. I understand.

582
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,639
I'll look for her myself.

583
00:37:21,769 --> 00:37:24,359
Actually, I've been to Ms. Zeng's office a few times,

584
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:26,439
but the receptionist kept saying she wasn't in.

585
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:27,519
She wouldn't let me in.

586
00:37:28,289 --> 00:37:30,920
I guess I've been blacklisted.

587
00:37:36,719 --> 00:37:38,679
Ms. Zeng is indeed on a business trip.

588
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:40,329
She'll be back in three days.

589
00:37:43,639 --> 00:37:44,639
I see.

590
00:37:44,809 --> 00:37:46,000
Thank you, Ms. Xin.

591
00:37:47,199 --> 00:37:50,360
(Rucheng Group)

592
00:38:08,519 --> 00:38:10,559
Ms. Zeng, I need to talk to you.

593
00:38:11,519 --> 00:38:12,960
I have nothing to say to you.

594
00:38:13,639 --> 00:38:14,856
I've been waiting here for you...

595
00:38:14,880 --> 00:38:17,360
because I wanted to tell you that Zhou Bin has returned to me.

596
00:38:17,599 --> 00:38:18,839
What do you want now?

597
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:19,999
You've misunderstood me.

598
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,599
I just want to tell you the truth.

599
00:38:23,119 --> 00:38:25,239
I can never be with Zhou Bin again.

600
00:38:25,289 --> 00:38:26,936
Do you really not love Zeng Cheng anymore?

601
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,640
Have you made up your mind to divorce her?

602
00:38:28,719 --> 00:38:29,769
Yes.

603
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:33,161
But she's still diligently trying to have a baby for you.

604
00:38:33,559 --> 00:38:34,639
It failed.

605
00:38:35,599 --> 00:38:36,809
She has given up too.

606
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:39,879
So you came to me because I'm young...

607
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:41,199
and can have children for you.

608
00:38:41,239 --> 00:38:42,679
Don't think of me as so superficial.

609
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,559
So when do you plan to get a divorce?

610
00:38:49,519 --> 00:38:50,679
I have it all arranged.

611
00:38:51,809 --> 00:38:52,856
At most, it will take a year.

612
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:55,000
If things go well, it could be as soon as six months.

613
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:58,000
Is this ring...

614
00:38:59,119 --> 00:39:00,519
a token of your promise?

615
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:01,880
Yes.

616
00:39:02,769 --> 00:39:04,119
Okay.

617
00:39:05,159 --> 00:39:06,679
I'll trust you one more time.

618
00:39:15,559 --> 00:39:18,480
The ring and recording can be used as evidence.

619
00:39:18,679 --> 00:39:19,718
If you need them...

620
00:39:19,719 --> 00:39:20,840
There's no need.

621
00:39:21,079 --> 00:39:22,329
You can get out now.

622
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,038
Ms. Zeng.

623
00:39:25,039 --> 00:39:27,199
I know our relationship is kind of awkward.

624
00:39:27,679 --> 00:39:29,809
You want to ruin my career and I accept that.

625
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:31,360
But please believe me.

626
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:33,079
I just want to stay away from Zhou Bin.

627
00:39:33,679 --> 00:39:35,039
Who wants to ruin your career?

628
00:39:35,639 --> 00:39:37,809
I've been rejected by several advertising agencies.

629
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:39,920
You hold a high status and have a lot of influence.

630
00:39:40,039 --> 00:39:41,639
I admit defeat. I deserve it.

631
00:39:43,519 --> 00:39:45,599
You've done all this, so why not just admit it?

632
00:39:45,809 --> 00:39:47,639
Which agencies? Tell me.

633
00:39:48,039 --> 00:39:49,159
I wouldn't resort...

634
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:51,480
to such despicable actions.

635
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:55,199
Could it be Zhou Bin?

636
00:39:56,599 --> 00:39:59,199
He should know your friends at those advertising agencies.

637
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:02,159
He probably used your name to do it.

638
00:40:05,599 --> 00:40:06,599
Ms. Zeng,

639
00:40:06,679 --> 00:40:09,119
you're the only one who can help me get rid of him now.

640
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:11,289
Not holding it against you...

641
00:40:11,809 --> 00:40:13,289
is already my utmost kindness.

642
00:40:14,079 --> 00:40:15,400
Why should I help you?

643
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:24,039
You can keep the ring.

644
00:40:24,119 --> 00:40:25,159
Get out.

645
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:02,119
I was too presumptuous and reckless.

646
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:05,440
If I were her, I would have reacted the same way.

647
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:08,200
Although they don't love each other anymore,

648
00:41:08,440 --> 00:41:09,559
they're still married.

649
00:41:10,199 --> 00:41:11,199
To put it bluntly,

650
00:41:11,200 --> 00:41:13,080
they are just in a shared-interest partnership.

651
00:41:16,679 --> 00:41:18,440
Didn't you think about it?

652
00:41:18,599 --> 00:41:21,400
What would you do if she told Zhou Bin about this?

653
00:41:24,119 --> 00:41:25,329
I've already come this far.

654
00:41:25,360 --> 00:41:26,719
There's no turning back.

655
00:41:27,880 --> 00:41:30,161
I sent her those recordings, but she didn't say anything.

656
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:34,920
I've made up my mind.

657
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:37,079
If Zhou Bin still texts me,

658
00:41:37,119 --> 00:41:38,559
that means she's hiding it from him.

659
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:41,400
I'll forward all the messages to her.

660
00:41:42,769 --> 00:41:44,039
I guess that's the only way.
